Package com.google.providerhelper

Class Summary
Builder Builds an object using fields extracted from an Android ContentProvider's Cursor object.
Reader<T extends Builder> Provides a java-style iterator over objects retrieved from rows of an Android ContentProvider; the objects' class must extend Builder.
